  "key": "Recommendation",
  "value": "Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/sql/instances/vegangenius-db/overview?project\u003dcomdottasteslikegood and click \"Edit\". Under the \"Database flags\" section, set the \"log_checkpoints\" database flag with the value \"On\"."
},{
  "key": "ExceptionInstructions",
  "value": "Add the security mark \"allow_sql_log_checkpoints_disabled\" to the asset with a value of \"true\" to prevent this finding from being activated again."
},{
  "key": "Explanation",
  "value": "Enabling \"log_checkpoints\" causes checkpoints and restart points to be logged in the server log. Some statistics are included in the log messages, including the number of buffers written and the time spent writing them."
},{
