[{
  "key": "Recommendation",
  "value": "Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/sql/instances/vegangenius-db/overview?project\u003dcomdottasteslikegood and click \"Edit\". Under the \"Database flags\" section, set the \"log_lock_waits\" database flag with the value \"On\"."
},{
  "key": "ExceptionInstructions",
  "value": "Add the security mark \"allow_sql_log_lock_waits_disabled\" to the asset with a value of \"true\" to prevent this finding from being activated again."
},{
  "key": "Explanation",
  "value": "Enabling the \"log_lock_waits\" setting creates log entries when a session waits longer than \"deadlock_timeout\" to acquire a lock. The logs are useful in determining if lock waits are causing poor performance."
},{
