  "value": "Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/sql/instances/vegangenius-db/overview?project\u003dcomdottasteslikegood and click \"Edit\". Under the \"Database flags\" section, set the \"log_temp_files\" database flag with the value \"0\"."
},{
  "key": "ExceptionInstructions",
  "value": "Add the security mark \"allow_sql_log_temp_files\" to the asset with a value of \"true\" to prevent this finding from being activated again."
},{
  "key": "Explanation",
  "value": "Temporary files can be created for sorts, hashes, and temporary query results. Setting the \"log_temp_files\" flag to \"0\" causes all temporary files information to be logged. Logging all temporary files is useful to identifying potencial performance issues."
},{
